{"tid":1805710,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"我宣布每年嘅倒數改變為「光復香港 時代革命」","createTime":"2019-12-31T18:30:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-01T05:28:57.000Z","uid":154875,"like":431,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"a26074e9732784db83dd608ebd4c469821d49ca8","tid":1805710,"uid":154875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T18:30:59.000Z","msg":"每一年倒數<br />\n我都覺得倒數唔係太重要<br />\n但係今年嘅我對個十秒好重視<br />\n<br />\n依場運動<br />\n我地唔知最後輸定贏<br />\n但係我地都要記住依場歷史<br />\n<br />\n我地將抗爭融入生活<br />\n當每一年嘅完結<br />\n我地都可以透過依句<br />\n去提一提我地<br />\n香港曾經有過一段咁嘅時間<br />\n有過一場革命<br />\n一場對自由空氣嘅追求<br />\n<br />\n我地要明白<br />\n共產黨唔會咁快倒台<br />\n我地一定要同佢鬥長命<br />\n我都好想佢俾我地依個奇蹟嘅小地方<br />\n可以用半年到一年嘅時間打倒<br />\n但百足之蟲 死而不僵<br />\n佢就算已經俾我地扣左99%血<br />\n佢個1%血都仲可以俾佢玩多十年<br />\n甚至二十，三十年<br />\n<br />\n返校嘅故事提到<br />\n女主角同男主角講<br />\n台灣近40年嘅白色恐怖<br />\n點都要有人記住依家享受嘅自由有幾可貴<br />\n我敢講我一定會記得<br />\n但只有我一個唔夠<br />\n每年31號提提大家<br />\n爭取自由嘅血與淚<br />\n警暴下嘅無助<br />\n司法制度下嘅逼害<br />\n<br />\n如果年年都係咁樣倒數<br />\n好肯定所有嘅新聞都會提我地<br />\nTvb都冇得唔報<br />\n我想大家同我做一個約定<br />\n2020年12月31日<br />\n同今日一樣<br />\n10，9，<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光，復，香，港<br />\n時，代，革，命</span></span></strong><br />\n手足，應承我好冇？<br />\n<br />\n最後，我想講<br />\n我地可以同共產黨打咁耐<br />\n係因為我地嘅團結<br />\n聽日1，1日<br />\n我想見到你地<br />\n都係個句<br />\n不是有了希望才堅持<br />\n是堅持了才會有希望<br />\n<br />\nNever forget <br />\nNever forgive <br />\nNever give up<br />\n<br />\n幫幫手，入去順手禁埋，反正你都睇左我咁耐嘅野<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原來聯署只係爭2000幾人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1805658\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1805658</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今次試下開社評台<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"788018ea731451e2bc98a1364e8f58f579aee6d0","tid":1805710,"uid":154875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T18:31:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"da4c4b54d653f6294714d5d1fb22bec7510ddb38","tid":1805710,"uid":154875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T18:32:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"29ea52c6ee8835f8f954d2bf8fdfd49a3704b603","tid":1805710,"uid":7168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T18:34:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86ca3fcebe8b8f6a0957fb6bcbb1c114a8e16bcf","tid":1805710,"uid":266130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T18:35:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2ee492df6eeaf7ae94f43652c61d4062df32965d","tid":1805710,"uid":248091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T18:38:02.000Z","msg":"一定到"},{"pid":"91161ccbd823ff3999acd6122c6c2e9709f94f2e","tid":1805710,"uid":236878,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T18:40:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />年年嗌?不了<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23ff582aa54984b08ff8b58a426e9148ab0cab20","tid":1805710,"uid":154875,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T18:40:56.000Z","msg":"將依句說話<br />\n變到好似新年咁<br />\n恭喜發財<br />\n30年後啲新香港人都會知依個歷史<br />\n都叫有小小用"},{"pid":"fa9de27c6e9e9a57e0432e3b0f7d53251f91e0d0","tid":1805710,"uid":154875,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"quote":{"pid":"91161ccbd823ff3999acd6122c6c2e9709f94f2e","tid":1805710,"uid":236878,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T18:40:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />年年嗌?不了<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T18:42:42.000Z","msg":"成日話支爆支爆<br />\n但其實好難<br />\n我覺得至少要10年<br />\n<br />\n同依個方法係令大家記住依樣野<br />\n香港人，好善忘"},{"pid":"b22fc32999079af623711bfe095f6dec9d67189f","tid":1805710,"uid":3406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T18:43:13.000Z","msg":"<