 />\n到底連登應承左人幾多樣嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"185f228c03f820a24fc6a03062bd18ea729c7962","tid":1805710,"uid":154875,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"e96d6275e7474a388b62112df14c99a411bd8a1b","tid":1805710,"uid":154875,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"45c62e42bbcba7fe2138ac025242b8666091ae11","tid":1805710,"uid":100550,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T18:52:27.000Z","msg":"我吊你啦 你覺得個八個大字係口號黎 叫下春？ <br />\n光復香港 用多一日黎光復都嫌多<br />\n仲要每年都叫？ 光撚復左仲洗叫？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T18:55:56.000Z","msg":"你真係覺得光復左<br />\n就代表你唔洗記住佢咩<br />\n退一步<br />\n你真係覺得咁易打得底共產黨？<br />\n依家係政權，警暴，法治<br />\n都係對家捉撚住你黎屌<br />\n<br />\n一年叫一次唔代表對依件事<br />\n快樂左<br />\n而係一種方法令我地記住"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T18:59:21.000Z","msg":"依一場運動，我地失去左咁多野<br />\n唔係光復左就唔需要記下話<br />\n你諗下個班被自殺嘅手足<br />\n光復左就當人condom啊<br />\n我同你講<br />\n屌你老母<br />\n光復完更加而記住啊<br />\n自由係用血淚爭取嫁"},{"pid":"26f79edf5b14a175916a47af81da5d97d1908e1c","tid":1805710,"uid":154875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da03d939595dddc9834778bc130db0c027f4e9bc","tid":1805710,"uid":1865,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T18:56:49.000Z","msg":"又應承我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到底連登應承左人幾多樣嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T19:00:25.000Z","msg":"咁你應承我<br />\n永不原諒死黑警<br />\n永不忘記班手足<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27782a8fa6054117118e062c12b136f39c6becfb","tid":1805710,"uid":154875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T19:04:37.000Z","msg":"我覺得有人唔同意好正常<br />\n但請用理據說服<br />\n是但講句屌你老母<br />\n邊個唔識<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd1471c5f0cc82b6227744363901d75426f40121","tid":1805710,"uid":1548