 />\n<br />\n如果年年都係咁樣倒數<br />\n好肯定所有嘅新聞都會提我地<br />\nTvb都冇得唔報<br />\n我想大家同我做一個約定<br />\n2020年12月31日<br />\n同今日一樣<br />\n10，9，<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光，復，香，港<br />\n時，代，革，命</span></span></strong><br />\n手足，應承我好冇？<br />\n<br />\n最後，我想講<br />\n我地可以同共產黨打咁耐<br />\n係因為我地嘅團結<br />\n聽日1，1日<br />\n我想見到你地<br />\n都係個句<br />\n不是有了希望才堅持<br />\n是堅持了才會有希望<br />\n<br />\nNever forget <br />\nNever forgive <br />\nNever give up<br />\n<br />\n幫幫手，入去順手禁埋，反正你都睇左我咁耐嘅野<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原來聯署只係爭2000幾人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1805658\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1805658</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今次試下開社評台<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T19:16:01.000Z","msg":"可以，一定到，<br />\n但係我地約係煲底倒數嗌好無？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf0e34a8bcbe85239ae91c08d30903d76777b310","tid":1805710,"uid":236878,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fa9de27c6e9e9a57e0432e3b0f7d53251f91e0d0","tid":1805710,"uid":154875,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"quote":{"pid":"91161ccbd823ff3999acd6122c6c2e9709f94f2e","tid":1805710,"uid":236878,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T18:40:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />年年嗌?不了<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T18:42:42.000Z","msg":"成日話支爆支爆<br />\n但其實好難<br />\n我覺得至少要10年<br />\n<br />\n同依個方法係令大家記住依樣野<br />\n香港人，好善忘"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T19:19:07.000Z","msg":"我明啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw其實每逢節日都可以同運動掛勾咁過<br />\n唔係剩係新年 <br />\n之前中秋節食印口號月餅<img 