動好成功<br />\n所以可以年年都搞<br />\n因為就算我地唔叫<br />\n都總有人會倒數<br />\n點解唔令佢變成依場運動一部分<br />\n農曆新年，清明，重陽到時再諗<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8b4e54a461e5e6dd953d7201fabf853aecedb10","tid":1805710,"uid":154875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a640a981f3b15a6ee6377d0f66175ec6ef506034","tid":1805710,"uid":247905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T19:23:57.000Z","msg":"以為影相唔舉V字<br />\n舉🖐👆"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T19:30:15.000Z","msg":"都唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"722fc571dbbd9e2fb3915c865375ae15c1d32ffa","tid":1805710,"uid":189306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T19:31:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff210c6a2b2533a83ec7a56f0bd3ea97512328ba","tid":1805710,"uid":135661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T19:34:04.000Z","msg":"每年嗌 姐係仲要有幾多手足死................."},{"pid":"b1b56f67360db61a79308c275f829b8e9eb21283","tid":1805710,"uid":249705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T19:35:23.000Z","msg":"Push<br />\n香港人對極權嘅抗爭係永遠唔可以完"},{"pid":"852169dc3d8ab882728e09ae739ab7d8a40f0b09","tid":1805710,"uid":154875,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"af7ea49387746a52f16210e51386435fc4344ac7","tid":1805710,"uid":236878,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e4a435bff22bcacce7fb3ebc37389082da5a9ab8","tid":1805710,"uid":258696,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"91161ccbd823ff3999acd6122c6c2e9709f94f2e","tid":1805710,"uid":236878,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T18:40:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />年年嗌?不了<br /