heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成件事冇影響<br />\n叫完唔會死多個<br />\n但你唔叫都會有一班人繼續倒數<br />\n咁點解唔做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6314b8a2fbd33974ee35f8fd1c0f5228e29720e8","tid":1805710,"uid":154875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49e83304de7adfa344e245202517a29064e048a3","tid":1805710,"uid":312881,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T19:37:23.000Z","msg":"希望今年係<br />\n「光！復！香！港！時！代！革！命！<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">成！功</span>」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T19:41:05.000Z","msg":"但轉左口號好似怪怪地<br />\nbtw希望成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2adcb1b5e7249e032cf1fff133224db2078645e9","tid":1805710,"uid":116568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T19:50:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"787e98ce4f51d40e9e4de2a40c4514d385a2a392","tid":1805710,"uid":158888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T19:51:32.000Z","msg":"一定要繼續堅持<br />\n直至真正光復"},{"pid":"f3876780b32e5e0c1d46dce35ac2e9877bf68735","tid":1805710,"uid":148203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T19:51:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24c07e13a248baf18616d5348e96137ce4f7e87d","tid":1805710,"uid":154875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"787e98ce4f51d40e9e4de2a40c4514d385a2a392","tid":1805710,"uid":158888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T19:51:32.000Z","msg":"一定要繼續堅持<br />\n直至真正光復"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T19:53:14.000Z","msg":"一直唔可以忘記<br />\n真正光復左<br />\n就當佢一個記念嘅行動啦<img src=\"/assets